      "description": "Experience a true, competition-quality game with the Whistler ping pong table. The consistently even surface delivers a reliable bounce across the table, keeping rallies smooth and every point decided by skill. Solid, stable, and refined in design, the Whistler pairs professional-level play with a sleek look suited to modern interiors.\nBEST FOR\nCrafted for indoor environments, the Whistler combines certified tournament performance with the freedom to practice and improve on your own time.\nIndoor table (Not weatherproof)\nFor national and international tournaments\nCan be used in the playback position for solo play\nEuropean standard: EN-Norm 14468-1\nTABLETOP\nPrecision-finished for performance and durability, the Whistler&rsquo;s thick playing surface and reinforced frame deliver a refined feel and dependable stability every time you play.\nChipboard 25mm\nColour: Green & Blue\nMulti-coated\nFrame profile A-60mm, powder-coated\nUNDERCARRIAGE\nThoughtfully engineered for everyday convenience, the Whistler combines a compact footprint, effortless mobility, and precise leveling for a stable, confidence-inspiring setup in any room.\nCompact (type 4b)\nRectangle-tube-profile 40 x 40 mm, square-profile 40 x 10 / 20 x 10 mm, powder-coated\n4 double wheels\nBalance of different standing positions and unevenness up to 25mm through height adjustment on the outer legs\nNET SET\nFinished with a high-quality, adjustable net that stays perfectly aligned and tensioned, delivering a refined, competition-level playing experience.\nPerfect-II-EN-stationary-compact\nHigh-quality net with stable post\nNet height-adjustable with clamp\nPlastic-coated\nNet: High-quality cotton net by type Weltmeister in green, blue or grey (depending on the color of the table top)\nStretching cord with chain for tightening the upper edge of the net\nMeasurement: 180cm x 15,2cm\nLOCKING SYSTEM\nIntuitively designed for ease and safety, the Whistler features a single-handle release and automatic locking system for smooth transitions and peace of mind every time.\nHandle system with metal handle underneath the tabletop unlocks both of the safety devices simultaneously\nSimple and automatic click-mechanism in storage and playing position of the table\nWHEELS\nDesigned for effortless mobility and dependable stability, the Whistler glides smoothly into place and locks down securely when it&rsquo;s time to play.\n4 double wheels 100mm with rubber tread\nAll wheels are manoeuvrable\n2 of them are lockable\nFind more at: tigerpingpong.",
